heading: Shadowed Plunge Dungeon Guide
content: Shadowed Plunge has a straightforward layout and hosts dangerous Nagari (Snakes) that have a couple of attacks that are difficult to avoid. It is tough to farm and has high XP monsters, but is not currently a possible . There is no boss in this dungeon; once you destroy the 3 Wards of Eyes at the end, the dungeon is complete. This dungeon unlocks the , a solid offensive aspect for a Bow Rogue. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! This dungeon is not accessible until you cleanse the evil in . This unlocks the Dungeon along with vendors and a waypoint. This can be done solo, but goes by quicker with a group of friends. Reviewed by
